ReactorEE.pcomponents

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ReactorEE.pcomponents.PlantComponent
      • ReactorEE.pcomponents.Generator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Generator
extends PlantComponent
    Generator class is used to calculate the power output of the plant based on the current RPM of the Turbine. The generator is perfect, i.e. it never breaks.

    Lamprey
